{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 32,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 154.96,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.322,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, behold, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "32:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.502,
      "end": 5.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I suppose that ye ponder somewhat in your hearts",
      "verse": "32:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 5.84,
      "end": 10.252,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning that which ye should do after ye have entered in by the way.",
      "verse": "32:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 10.432,
      "end": 13.776,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, behold, why do ye ponder these things in your hearts?",
      "verse": "32:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 14.456,
      "end": 16.685,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do ye not remember that I said unto you",
      "verse": "32:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 16.865,
      "end": 19.466,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that after ye had received the Holy Ghost",
      "verse": "32:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 19.646,
      "end": 21.922,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye could speak with the tongue of angels?",
      "verse": "32:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 22.102,
      "end": 24.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, how could ye speak with the tongue of angels",
      "verse": "32:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 25.115,
      "end": 27.019,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it were by the Holy Ghost?",
      "verse": "32:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 27.699,
      "end": 30.393,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Angels speak by the power of the Holy Ghost;",
      "verse": "32:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 30.573,
      "end": 33.081,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they speak the words of Christ.",
      "verse": "32:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 33.261,
      "end": 35.119,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I said unto you,",
      "verse": "32:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 35.299,
      "end": 37.389,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "feast upon the words of Christ;",
      "verse": "32:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 37.569,
      "end": 42.677,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, the words of Christ will tell you all things what ye should do.",
      "verse": "32:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 43.357,
      "end": 46.19,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, now after I have spoken these words,",
      "verse": "32:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 46.37,
      "end": 48.274,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if ye cannot understand them",
      "verse": "32:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 48.454,
      "end": 50.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it will be because ye ask not,",
      "verse": "32:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 50.863,
      "end": 52.442,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither do ye knock;",
      "verse": "32:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 52.622,
      "end": 56.105,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, ye are not brought into the light,",
      "verse": "32:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 56.285,
      "end": 58.143,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but must perish in the dark.",
      "verse": "32:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 58.823,
      "end": 61.191,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, again I say unto you",
      "verse": "32:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 61.371,
      "end": 63.6,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if ye will enter in by the way,",
      "verse": "32:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 63.78,
      "end": 65.638,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and receive the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "32:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 65.818,
      "end": 68.697,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it will show unto you all things what ye should do.",
      "verse": "32:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 69.377,
      "end": 71.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, this is the doctrine of Christ,",
      "verse": "32:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 71.879,
      "end": 74.433,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there will be no more doctrine given",
      "verse": "32:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 74.613,
      "end": 78.421,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until after he shall manifest himself unto you in the flesh.",
      "verse": "32:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 78.601,
      "end": 82.363,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when he shall manifest himself unto you in the flesh,",
      "verse": "32:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 82.543,
      "end": 86.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the things which he shall say unto you shall ye observe to do.",
      "verse": "32:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 86.845,
      "end": 89.306,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, cannot say more;",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 89.486,
      "end": 91.762,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Spirit stoppeth mine utterance,",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 91.942,
      "end": 93.753,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I am left to mourn",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 93.933,
      "end": 95.419,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the unbelief,",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 95.599,
      "end": 97.039,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the wickedness,",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 97.219,
      "end": 98.752,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the ignorance,",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 98.932,
      "end": 101.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the stiffneckedness of men;",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 101.434,
      "end": 103.524,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they will not search knowledge,",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 103.704,
      "end": 105.887,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nor understand great knowledge,",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 106.067,
      "end": 108.621,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "when it is given unto them in plainness,",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 108.801,
      "end": 110.844,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even as plain as word can be.",
      "verse": "32:7",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 111.524,
      "end": 113.846,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "32:8",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 114.026,
      "end": 116.905,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I perceive that ye ponder still in your hearts;",
      "verse": "32:8",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 117.085,
      "end": 120.336,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it grieveth me that I must speak concerning this thing.",
      "verse": "32:8",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 120.516,
      "end": 123.117,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For if ye would hearken unto the Spirit",
      "verse": "32:8",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 123.297,
      "end": 125.48,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which teacheth a man to pray,",
      "verse": "32:8",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 125.66,
      "end": 127.657,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye would know that ye must pray;",
      "verse": "32:8",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 127.837,
      "end": 130.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the evil spirit teacheth not a man to pray,",
      "verse": "32:8",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 130.85,
      "end": 132.986,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but teacheth him that he must not pray.",
      "verse": "32:8",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 133.666,
      "end": 135.524,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, I say unto you",
      "verse": "32:9",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 135.704,
      "end": 137.562,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye must pray always,",
      "verse": "32:9",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 137.742,
      "end": 139.089,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and not faint;",
      "verse": "32:9",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 139.269,
      "end": 142.613,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye must not perform any thing unto the Lord",
      "verse": "32:9",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 142.793,
      "end": 145.765,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save in the first place ye shall pray unto the Father",
      "verse": "32:9",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 145.945,
      "end": 147.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the name of Christ,",
      "verse": "32:9",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 147.797,
      "end": 150.723,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he will consecrate thy performance unto thee,",
      "verse": "32:9",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 150.903,
      "end": 154.293,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that thy performance may be for the welfare of thy soul.",
      "verse": "32:9",
      "lineIndex": 58
    }
  ]
}